                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1372" type="given" value="JOHN THOMAS"></interp>JOHN THOMAS CHITTENDEN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a constable of Woolwich. I took the prisoner into custody, he had a bag with him—I found a book in the bag—he goes about with matches—the book was claimed that evening.</p>
